uired before touching the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 28, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo one should touch the Quran unless they are pure.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 13217 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Suyuti Ibn Abdul Barr said, \u201cAl-Shafi\u2019i, Al-Awza\u2019i, Abu Thawr, and Ahmad said the written Quran should\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33438,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/12\/umar-convinces-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":24985,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Mushaf: Umar convinces Abu Bakr to collect the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: Abu Bak sent for me after the people of Al-Yamamah were killed and Umar ibn al-Khattab was with him. Abu Bakr, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cUmar came to me and said that many reciters of the Quran were killed in the fighting at\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25799,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/22\/ayat-rajm-not-written-kitab\/","url_meta":{"origin":24985,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Rajm: Verse of stoning not meant to be in Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Kathir ibn al-Salt reported: Amr ibn al-\u2018As and Zayd ibn Thabit would write down the Quran. They passed over this verse, and Zayd said, \u201cI heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, say: The married old man and old woman, if they commit adultery, then stone\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2696,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/quran-sunnah-then-ijtihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":24985,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ijtihad: Judge with the Quran, Sunnah, then your opinion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Harith ibn 'Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, sent Mu\u2019adh to Yemen and he said, \u201cHow will you judge?\u201d Mu\u2019adh said, \u201cI will judge according to the Book of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWhat if it is not in the Book of Allah?\u201d Mu\u2019adh\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25022,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/13\/ask-allah-by-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":24985,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Ask only from Allah with the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 13, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Imran ibn Husayn reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever reads the Quran, let him ask